i < matches.length - 1; ) { if (matches[i + 1].start < matches[i].end) { matches.splice(i + 1, 1); // Remove the next match since it overlaps } else { i++; // Move to next match } } return matches; } function applyTooltips(str) { const matches = getTooltips(str); } else if (typeof obj[key] === 'object') { applyTooltipsToObject(obj[key]); // Recursive call } } } function modifytooltip(searchstring, newtooltip) { for (let x in tooltipList) { if (tooltipList[x]["searchString"] == searchstring) { tooltipList[x]["explanationText"] = newtooltip;
